{"id":3271,"date":"2018-06-15T15:31:48","date_gmt":"2018-06-15T13:31:48","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/test.amtm.org\/?page_id=3271"},"modified":"2023-12-07T14:49:24","modified_gmt":"2023-12-07T13:49:24","slug":"parrainages","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.amtm.org\/sengager\/parrainages\/","title":{"rendered":"Parrainages"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"special-heading vntd-heading heading-no-border heading-align-center\"><h3 class=\"special-heading-title\">Pourquoi parrainer ?<\/h3><p class=\"special-heading-subtitle\">\u00ab Participer, c&#039;est ce qui donne un sens \u00e0 ma vie. Un courrier, une photo, 30 \u20ac par mois,<br \/>\ncela semble peu ici, mais \u00e0 chaque mission, c&#039;est toujours le m\u00eame choc de voir que pour eux c&#039;est beaucoup. Ceux qui n&#039;avaient rien re\u00e7oivent l&#039;opportunit\u00e9 de construire leur vie. C&#039;est un tr\u00e8s bel \u00e9change, donner et recevoir tellement d&#039;une autre mani\u00e8re... \u00bb<br \/>\nSabine Jauffret, Directrice des Parrainages<\/p><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\u00a0\u00bbmiddle\u00a0\u00bb parallax=\u00a0\u00bbcontent-moving\u00a0\u00bb parallax_speed_bg=\u00a0\u00bb1.3&Prime; css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1532425549271{padding-top: 90px !important;padding-bottom: 90px !important;background-position: 0 0;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbright\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1494861044583{padding-top: 20px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column_text font_size=\u00a0\u00bbmedium\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #f6a305;\">Qui sont vos filleuls ?<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Avec AMTM, venez en aide \u00e0 des enfants, adolescents n\u00e9palais, indiens, bouthanais et tib\u00e9tais, mais aussi des personnes \u00e2g\u00e9es (souvent des tib\u00e9tains en exil).<\/p>\n<p>Aujourd&rsquo;hui, plus de 1 000 enfants et adultes en grande difficult\u00e9 ont vu leur vie transform\u00e9e gr\u00e2ce au parrainage. Mais des centaines de demandes restent encore insatisfaites.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb][vc_single_image image=\u00a0\u00bb3414&Prime; img_size=\u00a0\u00bb700&#215;600&Prime; css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1532442436069{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\u00a0\u00bbmiddle\u00a0\u00bb parallax=\u00a0\u00bbcontent-moving\u00a0\u00bb parallax_speed_bg=\u00a0\u00bb1.3&Prime; css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1532425549271{padding-top: 90px !important;padding-bottom: 90px !important;background-position: 0 0;background-repeat:-repeat !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb][vc_single_image image=\u00a0\u00bb3418&Prime; img_size=\u00a0\u00bb700&#215;600&Prime; css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1532445024181{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime; col_padding=\u00a0\u00bb2&Prime; col_padding_side=\u00a0\u00bbright\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1494861044583{padding-top: 20px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #f6a305;\">Votre filleul b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiera &#8230;<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"vntd-icon-list icon-list-simple icon-list-basic icon-list-color-gradient-2\"><ul class=\"icon-list\"><li><i class=\"fa fa-angle-right color-gradient-2\"><\/i>d&#039;une am\u00e9lioration de son habitat et de ses conditions de vie<\/li><li><i class=\"fa fa-angle-right color-gradient-2\"><\/i>d&#039;une alimentation r\u00e9guli\u00e8re et plus \u00e9quilibr\u00e9e<\/li><li><i class=\"fa fa-angle-right color-gradient-2\"><\/i>d&#039;un suivi m\u00e9dical par des m\u00e9decins locaux<\/li><li><i class=\"fa fa-angle-right color-gradient-2\"><\/i>d&#039;un acc\u00e8s \u00e0 l&#039;\u00e9cole (des fournitures scolaires ou des livres ou encore des cours d&#039;anglais...) ou \u00e0 un programme \u00e9ducatif propre \u00e0 sa culture (dans les monast\u00e8res-\u00e9coles)<\/li><li><i class=\"fa fa-angle-right color-gradient-2\"><\/i>d&#039;un soutien affectif. Une simple lettre en anglais de votre part suffit \u00e0 le remplir de joie. Ce lien lui redonne confiance et espoir en la vie.<\/li><\/ul><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row color_scheme=\u00a0\u00bbwhite\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1541626389720{padding-top: 70px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #f6a305 !important;}\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column]<div class=\"special-heading vntd-heading heading-no-border heading-align-center\"style=\"margin-bottom:55px;\"><h3 class=\"special-heading-title\">Devenez parrain en quelques clics<\/h3><\/div>[vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime;]<div class=\"vntd-icon-box vntd-content-element box-centered-basic icon-size-medium box-centered  icon-box-with-link\"><a href=\"mailto:parrainer@amtm.org\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"icon-box-icon color-custom\"style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><i class=\"vc_li vc_li-mail\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"icon-box-content\"><h5 class=\"icon-box-title\">Envoyez un mail \u00e0 parrainer@amtm.org<\/h5><p class=\"icon-description\">Pr\u00e9cisez votre adresse postale, un num\u00e9ro de t\u00e9l\u00e9phone et votre pr\u00e9f\u00e9rence, si vous en avez, pour le parrainage : un enfant (moins de 16 ans), un(e) adulte ou une personne \u00e2g\u00e9e (de 60 ans ou plus).<\/p><\/div><\/a><\/div>[\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime;]<div class=\"vntd-icon-box vntd-content-element box-centered-basic icon-size-medium box-centered  icon-box-with-link\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/media\/set\/?set=a.723216909852688&#038;type=3\" target=\"_blank\"><div clas